  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/5b98a24f5caa7d22364d73595c5e1dc9.webp?t=1768632877\" width=600 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/922e836904bb21ef89c202a062f50598.poster.avif?t=1768632877\" width=662 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/922e836904bb21ef89c202a062f50598.webm?t=1768632877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/922e836904bb21ef89c202a062f50598.mp4?t=1768632877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An ordinary worker goes on a business trip. Since the organization is experiencing financial difficulties, they rented him a house on the outskirts of the city. We are tired, driving to this house at night and don’t even suspect that otherworldly evil is waiting for us in the house, ready to devour us.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/4dd3f2011b2980a371216070c6415015.webp?t=1768632877\" width=600 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/0ea7d739c2f87a9ab5c2ca7167df391a.poster.avif?t=1768632877\" width=612 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/0ea7d739c2f87a9ab5c2ca7167df391a.webm?t=1768632877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/0ea7d739c2f87a9ab5c2ca7167df391a.mp4?t=1768632877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On your way you will encounter many challenging and unique puzzles, solve them to move further towards your goal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/630fe6ad57281eae3b68d424655ca11d.webp?t=1768632877\" width=600 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/32a8265aab7ad11496b70d67bb470231.poster.avif?t=1768632877\" width=612 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/32a8265aab7ad11496b70d67bb470231.webm?t=1768632877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/32a8265aab7ad11496b70d67bb470231.mp4?t=1768632877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for intense first-person horror where every step could be your last and every turn could lead to new, nightmarish discoveries.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/5b98a24f5caa7d22364d73595c5e1dc9.webp?t=1768632877\" width=600 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/922e836904bb21ef89c202a062f50598.poster.avif?t=1768632877\" width=662 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/922e836904bb21ef89c202a062f50598.webm?t=1768632877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/922e836904bb21ef89c202a062f50598.mp4?t=1768632877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An ordinary worker goes on a business trip. Since the organization is experiencing financial difficulties, they rented him a house on the outskirts of the city. We are tired, driving to this house at night and don’t even suspect that otherworldly evil is waiting for us in the house, ready to devour us.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/4dd3f2011b2980a371216070c6415015.webp?t=1768632877\" width=600 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/0ea7d739c2f87a9ab5c2ca7167df391a.poster.avif?t=1768632877\" width=612 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/0ea7d739c2f87a9ab5c2ca7167df391a.webm?t=1768632877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/0ea7d739c2f87a9ab5c2ca7167df391a.mp4?t=1768632877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On your way you will encounter many challenging and unique puzzles, solve them to move further towards your goal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/630fe6ad57281eae3b68d424655ca11d.webp?t=1768632877\" width=600 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/32a8265aab7ad11496b70d67bb470231.poster.avif?t=1768632877\" width=612 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/32a8265aab7ad11496b70d67bb470231.webm?t=1768632877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549430/extras/32a8265aab7ad11496b70d67bb470231.mp4?t=1768632877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for intense first-person horror where every step could be your last and every turn could lead to new, nightmarish discoveries.</p>",
